column1: Traffic reports will resume Thursday January 27 at 4:00 p.m.

column3: Traffic Alert for Versailles Rd at New Circle Rd:
column4: All inbound lanes shutdown due to a serious collision.  Traffic diverted to the outer loop of New Circle Rd.

column3: Traffic Alert for Versailles Rd at New Circle Rd:
column4: Outbound Versailles Rd left lane and turn lane also blocked.

column3: Traffic Alert for Versailles Rd at New Circle Rd:
column4: Update 10:43 a.m. - The roadway is being reopened.
